{"id": "art-15312", "label": "Art. 15312", "title": "Art. 15312", "slug": "art-15312", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1767390662\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2081\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1767390662\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>12</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_354148829\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2080\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_354148829\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Durata mandatului administratorilor, respectiv al\nmembrilor directoratului <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ai consiliului de\nsupraveghere, este stabilit&#259; prin actul constitutiv, ea neputând <span\nclass=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;i</span> 4 ani. Ei sunt reeligibili, când prin\nactul constitutiv nu se dispune altfel.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_462091612\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2079\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_462091612\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Durata mandatului primilor membri ai consiliului de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv al primilor membri ai\nconsiliului de supraveghere, nu poate <span class=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;i</span>\n2 ani.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1338502601\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2078\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1338502601\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Pentru ca numirea unui administrator, respectiv a unui\nmembru al directoratului sau al consiliului de supraveghere, s&#259; fie\nvalabil&#259; din punct de vedere juridic, persoana numit&#259; trebuie s&#259;\no accepte în mod expres.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_915032954\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2077\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_915032954\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Persoana numit&#259; în una dintre <span class=SpellE>func&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (3) trebuie s&#259; fie asigurat&#259; pentru\nr&#259;spundere profesional&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}